			 and</text>
				</paragraph>
        <paragraph id="ID1A5FC372D789421ABC42FCBABB5F3EA0">
          <enum>(3)</enum>
          <text>by striking
			 <quote>as adjusted by <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Legislative Reorganization Act of 1946/s:601/ss:a/p:2">paragraph (2)</cato:entity-ref> of this subsection</quote> and inserting
			 <quote>adjusted as provided by law</quote>.</text>
				</paragraph>
      </subsection>
